Summary:           Development files for %{name}

Requires:          %{name}%{?_isa}                                 =  %{version}-%{release}
Provides:          %{name}-devel                                =  %{version}-%{release}
Provides:          %{name}-devel%{?_isa}                        =  %{version}-%{release}

%description devel
