%{!?guile_extdir:  %global guile_extdir  %(pkg-config --variable=extensiondir %{guile_pkgconf})}

Summary:           Guile bindings for %{name}

BuildRequires:     guile-devel
BuildRequires:     pkgconfig
BuildRequires:     swig

Requires:          guile
Requires:          %{name}%{?_isa}                                 =  %{version}-%{release}

